<span title="老王力气大无穷 双手举起纸灯笼" class="bio">
老王力气大无穷 双手举起纸灯笼
</span>
</span>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="3313">



<span class="voters text"><span class="user-block"><a data-hovercard="p$t$marsliu" href="https://www.zhihu.com/people/marsliu" target="_blank" class="zg-link author-link" title="刘鑫"
>刘鑫</a></span>&nbsp;<a href="#" class="more text">等&nbsp;<span class="js-voteCount">3313</span>&nbsp;人赞同</a></span>


